item.title: CVE-2022-1539|2024-08-03T00:10:03.492Z -- unknown -- exports%20and%20reports
item.description: The Exports and Reports WordPress plugin before 0.9.2 does not sanitize and validate data when generating the CSV to export, which could lead to a CSV injection, by the use of Microsoft Excel DDE function, or to leak data via maliciously injected hyperlinks.
